collectors.titleDetails: (2 total Queries, 2 of them unique across 1 Connection)

queries.sql: SELECT `u`.`id_user`, `u`.`nama` AS `nama_karyawan`, COUNT(CASE WHEN t.tgl_selesai IS NULL THEN 1 END) AS task_on_progress, COUNT(CASE WHEN t.tgl_selesai IS NOT NULL AND t.tgl_selesai <= t.tgl_planing THEN 1 END) AS task_selesai, COUNT(CASE WHEN t.tgl_selesai IS NOT NULL AND t.tgl_selesai > t.tgl_planing THEN 1 END) AS task_overdue FROM `user` `u` LEFT JOIN `task` `t` ON `t`.`id_user` = `u`.`id_user` AND `t`.`deleted_at` IS NULL WHERE `u`.`deleted_at` IS NULL AND `u`.`id_usergroup` IS NOT NULL AND `u`.`user_level` IN ('staff','supervisi') GROUP BY `u`.`id_user` ORDER BY `u`.`nama` ASC

timelineData.query: SELECT `u`.`id_user`, `u`.`nama` AS `nama_karyawan`, COUNT(CASE WHEN t.tgl_selesai IS NULL THEN 1 END) AS task_on_progress, COUNT(CASE WHEN t.tgl_selesai IS NOT NULL AND t.tgl_selesai <= t.tgl_planing THEN 1 END) AS task_selesai, COUNT(CASE WHEN t.tgl_selesai IS NOT NULL AND t.tgl_selesai > t.tgl_planing THEN 1 END) AS task_overdue FROM `user` `u` LEFT JOIN `task` `t` ON `t`.`id_user` = `u`.`id_user` AND `t`.`deleted_at` IS NULL WHERE `u`.`deleted_at` IS NULL AND `u`.`id_usergroup` IS NOT NULL AND `u`.`user_level` IN ('staff','supervisi') GROUP BY `u`.`id_user` ORDER BY `u`.`nama` ASC
